sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Citizen
    participant FE as Frontend (PWA)
    participant API as Backend API
    participant AL as Audit Ledger
    participant AS as Anchor Service
    participant CB as Anchor Breaker
    participant RPC as Ethereum RPC
    participant SC as MultiSig + Anchor

    Note over CB: STATE = CLOSED (RPC healthy)

    U->>FE: register parcel
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/parcels
    API->>AL: append PARCEL_REGISTERED event
    AL-->>API: seq + hash
    API-->>FE: 201 + idempotency-key

    Note over RPC: Sepolia RPC fails<br/>(timeout or 5xx)

    AS->>RPC: commitBatch(root)
    RPC-->>AS: ERR / timeout
    AS->>CB: register_failure()
    Note over CB: STATE = OPEN

    rect rgba(180, 90, 90, 0.12)
        Note over AL,SC: Degraded mode — operations continue, anchors queue
        U->>FE: register more parcels
        FE->>API: POST /api/v1/parcels
        API->>AL: append events (still tamper-evident off-chain)
        AS->>CB: probe?
        CB-->>AS: OPEN, defer
        AS-->>AS: keep queue, retry every 30 s
    end

    Note over RPC: RPC recovers

    AS->>CB: probe()
    CB-->>AS: HALF_OPEN
    AS->>RPC: commitBatch(root)
    RPC-->>AS: tx hash
    AS->>SC: confirm 3-of-5 threshold
    SC-->>AS: receipt + block
    AS->>CB: register_success()
    Note over CB: STATE = CLOSED

    rect rgba(90, 150, 90, 0.12)
        Note over AS,SC: Queue drains. anchor_breaker → closed. UI flips to Chain live.
        AS->>AL: mark batch CONFIRMED
        FE-->>U: ChainStatusBeacon turns green
    end
